== Welcome ==
Hello '''SenakaFernando''', and [[Wikipedia:Welcome, newcomers|welcome]] to Wikipedia! We're really glad you've chosen to sign up for an account; it offers numerous [[Wikipedia:Why create an account?|benefits]] in case you weren't already aware of them.

Thankyou for [[Special:Contributions/SenakaFernando|your contributions]] if you've been editing before you got this message. If you haven't, don't worry: there are numerous ways you can contribute to Wikipedia if you're not sure where to start yet. Either way, we hope you'll like the place and decide to stay. '''We all remember what it's like to be new, so [[Wikipedia:Please do not bite the newcomers|don't let others scare you off]]'''.
