=== Contributing ===

With these references at hand, we hope you find it easier to contribute to Wikipedia. Here's a brief synopsis of some ways you can:

*We obviously wouldn't have an encyclopedia without articles. [[Wikipedia:Article development|This page]] shows how you can help them grow. 

*Removing [[Wikipedia:Vandalism|vandalism]] and keeping the integrity of articles intact is a great way of contributing. More information on how to do so can be found [[Wikipedia:Cleaning_up_vandalism|here]].

*Fixing typos, correcting poor grammar and repairing broken links are just some examples of useful, [[Wikipedia:WikiGnome|behind the scenes]] contributions. Even just making things [[Wikipedia:WikiFairy|look nice]] makes using Wikipedia more pleasant for everybody.

*If you like working with images, you might be interested in the [[Wikipedia:Graphic Lab|Graphic Lab]]. Similarly, [[Wikipedia:Picture tutorial|this page]] shows you how to work with images in Wikipedia articles.

*[[:Category:Wikipedia maintenance|This page]] lists the many types of tasks you can do to maintain Wikipedia.

*There are numerous WikiProjects that aim to provide coordination and collaboration on particular subjects. From [[Wikipedia:List of WikiProjects|this list]], you can join a project and contribute within an area that interests you.

